Julie is taking her pet rock, Rocko, for a walk. Rocko is safely fastened to the inside of a hollow cylinder with inner radius [`R=[$r]\ cm`] and thickness [`d=[$d]\ cm`]. If the point [`O`] at the center of the cylinder is moving at a constant velocity of [`-[$v]\hat{i}\ m/s`], what is the angular velocity of her pet rock?

[`\vec{\omega}=`][____]{"$angVel"} [`\hat{k}\ rad/s`]

What is the maximum speed her pet rock will experience at any point on its surface?

[`v_{max}=`][____]{"$v_max"} [`m/s`]

